## node-listen-udp-syslog

node-listen-udp-syslog is a modularized Syslog udp server for handling RFC5424 messages (http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc5424) over UDP (http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc5426)

## Running

app.js provides an example of how to include and configure the library, as well as process received udp syslog messages.

`node app.js`

will listen on port 1514 and echo messages to the console
